1891
04:02:45.500 --> 04:02:50.000
They wanted us to be proud of our heritage.

1892
04:02:50.000 --> 04:03:02.000
And so they sent my sisters and me to Venarini Academy in Worcester, Mass., a parochial school run by an order of Italian nuns.

1893
04:03:02.000 --> 04:03:06.000
I could tell you some really good stories.

1894
04:03:06.000 --> 04:03:22.000
