1895
04:03:22.000 --> 04:03:24.000
They had nothing left.

1896
04:03:24.000 --> 04:03:29.500
But it was important to them, so they made it work.

1897
04:03:29.500 --> 04:03:33.000
And I'm not against private schools either.

1898
04:03:33.000 --> 04:03:42.500
